 <PERSON> John-Thor </PERSON> <PERSON> Dahlburg </PERSON>, an <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> correspondent based in <LOCATION> Moscow </LOCATION> since November 1986, specializes in <LOCATION> Soviet </LOCATION> politics and internal affairs.
