<HEAD>URGENT</HEAD>
<HEAD>Sources Say it is ``Doubtful'' Fighter Was Shot Down</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By BRYAN BRUMLEY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
